file.name: converter.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: PDF Render api
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:3300
paths:
  '/.well-known/docs':
    get:
      summary: HTML Docs
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Index route with html docs
          content:
            text/html: {}

  '/.well-known/openapi.yaml':
    get:
      summary: API
      responses:
        '200':
          description: API Definition
          content:
            text/yaml: {}

  '/html':
    post:
      requestBody:
        description: The html content to render
        required: true
        content:
          text/html: {}
      summary: Generate PDF from html
      responses:
        'default': { $ref: '#/components/responses/HttpErrorResponse' }
        '200':
          description: PDF REsult
          content:
            application/pdf: {}

components:
  responses:
    HttpErrorResponse:
      description: Error Response
      content:
        application/json:
          schema: { $ref: '#/components/schemas/HttpError' }

  schemas:
    HttpError:
      properties:
        message:
          type: string
      additionalProperties: false

Error: notImplemented: path "/.well-known/docs": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/html]
